<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الشُّبْرُمَان:</span> نَبْتٌ أَو مَوْضِع.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ يَصِفُ حَمِيرًا:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(تَرفَعُ من كُلّ زُقاقٍ قَسْطَلَا ... )</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(فصَبَّحَت من شُبْرُمانَ مَنْهَلَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
